<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 50%, #0f172a 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      color: #e2e8f0;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }
    .landing-nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1.25rem 2rem;
      max-width: 1280px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .landing-nav .logo {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #38bdf8;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    .landing-nav .logo i { font-size: 1.75rem; }
    .landing-nav .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: center; }
    .landing-nav .nav-links a { 
      color: #94a3b8; 
      text-decoration: none; 
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .landing-nav .nav-links a:hover { color: #e2e8f0; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }
    .btn-landing {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      padding: 0.625rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    .btn-landing-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6, #2563eb);
      color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(59,130,246,0.3);
    }
    .btn-landing-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(59,130,246,0.4); }
    .btn-landing-outline {
      background: transparent;
      color: #e2e8f0;
      border: 1px solid #334155;
    }
    .btn-landing-outline:hover { border-color: #3b82f6; color: #38bdf8; }
    .btn-landing-lg {
      padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .hero {
      max-width: 1280px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: calc(100vh - 80px);
    }
    .hero-content h1 {
      font-size: 3.25rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.15;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e2e8f0 0%, #38bdf8 50%, #818cf8 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .hero-content p {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: #94a3b8;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .hero-buttons { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .hero-visual {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      position: relative;
    }
    .hero-card {
      background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.7);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      border: 1px solid #334155;
      border-radius: 1.25rem;
      padding: 2.5rem;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 480px;
      box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    }
    .hero-card .stat-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .hero-card .stat-item {
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6);
      border-radius: 0.75rem;
      padding: 1rem;
      text-align: center;
      border: 1px solid #1e293b;
    }
    .hero-card .stat-item .num {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #38bdf8;
    }
    .hero-card .stat-item .label {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #64748b;
      margin-top: 0.25rem;
    }
    .hero-card .question-preview {
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6);
      border-radius: 0.75rem;
      padding: 1.25rem;
      border: 1px solid #1e293b;
    }
    .hero-card .question-preview .q-text {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #cbd5e1;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .hero-card .question-preview .options { display: grid; gap: 0.5rem; }
    .hero-card .question-preview .opt {
      padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
      background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.5);
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #94a3b8;
    }
    .hero-card .question-preview .opt.correct {
      background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.15);
      border: 1px solid rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.3);
      color: #4ade80;
    }

    .features-section {
      max-width: 1280px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
    }
    .features-section h2 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      color: #f1f5f9;
    }
    .features-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .feature-card {
      background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.5);
      border: 1px solid #1e293b;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      padding: 1.75rem;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }
    .feature-card:hover {
      border-color: #3b82f6;
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.8);
    }
    .feature-card i {
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: #38bdf8;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .feature-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #e2e8f0;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .feature-card p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #64748b;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .footer-landing {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      color: #475569;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 2rem 1rem; text-align: center; }
      .hero-content h1 { font-size: 2.25rem; }
      .hero-buttons { justify-content: center; }
      .landing-nav { padding: 1rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="landing-nav">
    <div class="logo">
      <i class="fas fa-bolt"></i> PowerPlant Quiz
    </div>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="#features">Features</a>
      <a href="/login">Sign In</a>
      <a href="/register" class="btn-landing btn-landing-primary">
        <i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i> Get Started
      </a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Master Power Plant & Mechanical Engineering</h1>
      <p>
        Prepare for licensure exams with our comprehensive question bank covering Power Plant Engineering, 
        Industrial Plant Design, Thermodynamics, Heat Transfer, Refrigeration, and Air Conditioning. 
        Practice with real exam-style questions, track your progress, and ace your boards.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-buttons">
        <a href="/register" class="btn-landing btn-landing-primary btn-landing-lg">
          <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i> Start Free Trial
        </a>
        <a href="/login" class="btn-landing btn-landing-outline btn-landing-lg">
          <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i> Sign In
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-visual">
      <div class="hero-card">
        <div class="stat-grid">
          <div class="stat-item">
            <div class="num">500+</div>
            <div class="label">Questions</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <div class="num">6</div>
            <div class="label">Modules</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <div class="num">3</div>
            <div class="label">Difficulty Levels</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <div class="num">24/7</div>
            <div class="label">Practice Access</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="question-preview">
          <div class="q-text">What is the efficiency of a Carnot cycle operating between 800°C and 30°C?</div>
          <div class="options">
            <div class="opt">A. 55.2%</div>
            <div class="opt correct">B. 71.7%</div>
            <div class="opt">C. 68.4%</div>
            <div class="opt">D. 62.1%</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="features-section" id="features">
    <h2>Why PowerPlant Quiz?</h2>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i>
        <h3>Comprehensive Question Bank</h3>
        <p>Hundreds of carefully curated multiple-choice questions covering all major ME subjects with detailed explanations.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
        <h3>Track Your Progress</h3>
        <p>Monitor your performance with detailed analytics, identify weak areas, and improve your scores over time.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt"></i>
        <h3>Customizable Quizzes</h3>
        <p>Filter questions by module, topic, and difficulty level. Create practice tests that match your study needs.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <i class="fas fa-user-graduate"></i>
        <h3>Exam-Focused Content</h3>
        <p>Questions modeled after actual licensure exams. Covers PRC board exam topics for Mechanical Engineers.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
        <h3>Responsive Design</h3>
        <p>Study anywhere, anytime. Fully responsive design works on desktop, tablet, and mobile devices.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
        <h3>Secure & Private</h3>
        <p>Your data is protected with industry-standard encryption. Secure authentication keeps your account safe.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer-landing">
    <p>&copy; <script>document.write(new Date().getFullYear())</script> PowerPlant Quiz. All rights reserved. Built for Mechanical Engineering excellence.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>

